68    /**
69    * Base class representing a data series. Subclasses are left to implement the
70    * actual data structures.
71    * <P>
72    * The series has two properties ("Key" and "Description") for which you can
73    * register a <code>PropertyChangeListener</code>.
74    * <P>
75    * You can also register a {@link SeriesChangeListener} to receive notification
76    * of changes to the series data.
77    */
